{
  "key": "noc-proposal-letter",
  "config": {
    "defaultStyle": {
      "font": "Cambay"
    },
    "content": [

      {
        "style": "noc-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": [
            50, "*"
          ],
          "body": [
            [{
                "image": "{{logo}}",
                "width": 50,
                "margin": [8, 10, 10, 0]
              },
              {
                "stack": [{
                    "text": "{{header}}",
                    "style": "receipt-logo-header"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "{{colony_branch}}",
                    "style": "receipt-logo-sub-header"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "New Deluxe Building, Sector 17-E, Chandigarh",
                    "style": "receipt-logo-sub-header"
                  }
                ],
                "alignment": "center",
                "margin": [
                  0,
                  12,
                  0,
                  0
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 20, 0, 0],
        "columns": [{
            "text": "Sub:-",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "bold": true,
            "width": "auto",
            "alignment": "left"

          },
          {
            "margin": [20, 0, 0, 0],
            "width": "*",
            "text": "Issue of NOC for water &amp; Sewerage connections in respect of House No {{houseNumber}},Chandigarh. ",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "bold": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 20, 0, 0],
        "style": "pdfContent",
        "text": [{
            "text": "A PUC letter received from "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{ownerName}} ",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": " R/o "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{address}} H.No. {{houseNumber}} {{village}} {{mohalla}} ",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": " Chandigarh vide this office diary No. _____dated ________ along with enclosures on the subject cited above."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 20, 0, 0],
        "style": "pdfContent",
        "text":[
          {
            "text": "In this regard, the applicant requested to obtain the NOC for the issue of new water & Sewerage connections in respect of House No. "
          },
          {
            "text":"{{houseNumber}}, {{village}}, {{mohalla}}",
            "bold":true
          },
          {
            "text":" Chandigarh. The consumers who had applied for new water & sewerage connections on the basis of related documents i.e Patwari report, Area Sarpanch report along with other documents, and further stated that the complete case along with application is forwarded for necessary action. The applicant "
          },
          {
            "text":"{{ownerName}} ",
            "bold":true
          },
          {
            "text":" has complete documents as per check list for water sewerage connections. Now the case forwarded to area J.E for site verification."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 20, 0, 0],
        "style": "pdfContent",
        "text": "Submitted Please"
      }
    ],
    "styles": {
      "pdfContent": {
        "color": "#000000",
        "bold": false,
        "fontSize": 11,
        "fontWeight": 400,
        "margin": [
          3,
          0,
          0,
          0
        ]
      },
      "pt-reciept-citizen-header": {
        "fontSize": 12,
        "bold": true,
        "margin": [
          0,
          8,
          0,
          0
        ],
        "color": "#484848"
      },
      "receipt-logo-header": {
        "color": "#484848",
        "fontSize": 14,
        "bold": true,
        "letterSpacing": 0.74,
        "margin": [
          0,
          0,
          0,
          5
        ]
      },
      "receipt-logo-sub-header": {
        "color": "#484848",
        "fontFamily": "Roboto",
        "fontSize": 13,
        "letterSpacing": 1.6,
        "margin": [
          0,
          6,
          0,
          0
        ]
      },
      "noc-head": {
        "margin": [
          -25,
          -25,
          0,
          1
        ]
      }

    }
  }
}